data.comment: The match is underway in Solna.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
In the minute 2, Throw-in for AIK in the half of Ostersund.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards Ostersund a goal kick.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 3, Ostersund are coming forward and Blair Turgott gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
Goal kick for AIK at Friends Arena.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 6, AIK pushes forward through Nabil Bahoui, whose finish on goal is saved.
Throw-in AIK.
Throw-in for Ostersund at Friends Arena.
In the minute 8, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a throw-in for AIK, close to Ostersund's area.
Ostersund have a goal kick.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a Ostersund throw-in in AIK's half.
In the minute 10, Throw-in for AIK in their own half.
Throw-in high up the field for AIK in Solna.
AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 13, Corner awarded to AIK.
Heradi Rashidi for AIK drives towards goal at Friends Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Ostersund to take a throw-in in AIK territory.
In the minute 15, Ball safe as Ostersund is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a Ostersund throw-in in AIK's half.
Can Ostersund capitalize from this throw-in deep inside AIK's half?
In the minute 19, Throw-in for AIK in their own half.
Can Ostersund get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in AIK's half?
Ostersund awarded a free kick in their own half.

Free kick Ostersund.
Felix Michel Melki (AIK) has received a first yellow card.

It's a goal kick for the home team in Solna.
Ostersund attack but Ludvig Fritzson's header doesn't find the target.
In the minute 25, Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
Goal! Ludvig Fritzson gives Ostersund a 0-1 lead.
Nebiyou Perry with an assist there.
In the minute 28, Felix Michel Melki is writhing in pain and play has been suspended for a few moments.
Free kick for AIK in the half of Ostersund.
Bartosz Grzelak (AIK) is making a first change, with Enock Kofi Adu replacing the possibly injured Felix Michel Melki.
In the minute 30, Throw-in for AIK at Friends Arena.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to AIK.
In Solna a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 34, AIK have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
In Solna AIK attack through Per Karlsson. The finish is off target, however.
Corner awarded to AIK.
In the minute 35, Kaspar Sjoberg awards Ostersund a goal kick.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards the home team a throw-in.
AIK have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
In the minute 38, Throw-in for AIK close to the penalty box.
Throw-in for AIK in the half of Ostersund.
AIK have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 39, Ball goes out of play for a Ostersund goal kick.
AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In Solna a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 42, Isak Ssewankambo of Ostersund gets in a strike, but is off target.
AIK have a goal kick.
Throw-in AIK.
In the minute 43, Goal kick for AIK at Friends Arena.
AIK are pushing forward but Nabil Bahoui's finish is wide of the goal.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Solna.
In the minute 44, Corner awarded to AIK.
Ostersund's Rewan Amin misses with an attempt on goal.
Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
In the minute 45, Ostersund's Rewan Amin is on target but unsuccessful.
Kaspar Sjoberg will wait an extra 1 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 1st half.
The first-half is over.
In the minute 46, The whistle has gone to start the second-half.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
Bartosz Grzelak is making the team's second substitution at Friends Arena with Kolbeinn Sigthorsson replacing Henok Goitom.
In the minute 47, AIK's Nabil Bahoui gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards Ostersund a goal kick.
AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 50, AIK to take a throw-in in Ostersund territory.
Ostersund needs to be cautious. AIK have an attacking throw-in.

The match has been stopped briefly for attention to the injured Aly Keita.
AIK make their third substitution with Sebastian Larsson replacing Ebenezer Ofori.
In the minute 56, Aly Keita returns to the field for Ostersund after picking up a slight injury.
Ostersund are pushing forward but Noah Sonko Sundberg's finish is wide of the goal.
Corner awarded to Ostersund.
In the minute 57, It's a goal kick for the away team in Solna.
Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Kolbeinn Sigthorsson (AIK) strikes at Friends Arena but his header is cleared.
In the minute 60, Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
Ostersund's Isak Ssewankambo gets in a shot but it is blocked by a AIK defender.
Ludvig Fritzson (Ostersund) goes close with a header but the ball is scrambled away by AIK defenders.
In the minute 62, Rasmus Lindkvist is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
AIK's Rasmus Lindkvist looks ok and returns to the pitch.
Free kick AIK.
In the minute 65, Ostersund have a goal kick.
Throw-in AIK.
Kolbeinn Sigthorsson (AIK) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 66, Ball goes out of play for a Ostersund goal kick.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a AIK throw-in in Ostersund's half.
Stefan Silva is on a sub for Heradi Rashidi for AIK.
In the minute 70, It seems as if Rasmus Lindkvist is unable to continue. Eric Kahl replaces him for the home team.
Throw-in for Ostersund in their own half.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
In the minute 72, Goal kick for Ostersund at Friends Arena.
Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
In the minute 74, Jerell Sellars is replacing Blair Turgott for Ostersund at Friends Arena.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Solna.
Can Ostersund get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in AIK's half?
In the minute 76, Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
Ostersund awarded a free kick in their own half.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to AIK.
In the minute 78, At Friends Arena, Rewan Amin has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Ostersund needs to be cautious. AIK have an attacking throw-in.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
In the minute 80, Free kick for Ostersund in the half of AIK.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards the home team a throw-in.
AIK drive upfield and Eric Kahl gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Ostersund defender.
In the minute 81, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Ostersund.
Isak Ssewankambo of Ostersund gets in a strike, but is off target.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards AIK a goal kick.
In the minute 84, AIK to take a throw-in in Ostersund territory.
The away team have replaced Ludvig Fritzson with Sam Mensiro. This is the second substitution made today by Amir Azrafshan.
Ronald Mukiibi is replacing Kalpi Ouattara for the away team.
In the minute 85, Throw-in high up the field for AIK in Solna.
Free kick in a good position for Ostersund!
Per Karlsson AIK.
In the minute 87, In Solna a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Eirik Haugan (Ostersund) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Corner awarded to AIK.
5 minutes of injury time will be added to the 2nd half.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
Can Ostersund capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
Throw-in for AIK at Friends Arena.
The second-half is over. The match ends 0-1.
Amir Azrafshan (Ostersund) is making a fourth substitution, with Henrik Bellman replacing Nebiyou Perry.
Noah Sonko Sundberg (Ostersund) has been shown a straight red card by referee Kaspar Sjoberg.
Enock Kofi Adu is booked for the home team.
